Package contains 18 grids. 3/8 Limestone gravel recommended to fill the grid. 3/4-In to 1-in angular gravel is recommended for sub base. Strong permeable paver system for residential vehicular drive ways or parking spots. Fast and easy to build. Eco-friendly 100% recycled plastic and natural water filter.
